import numpy as np

from sympy import *

fig, ax=plt.subplots()

# Open Cable Fitting 

def opcab (f,b,s,p):
    return -50/np.tan((f+p)*b)+s

param, param_cov = curve_fit(opcab, f, z.real,bounds=((0,-np.inf,0),(.05,np.inf,np.inf)))
param

def loaded_re (f,b,Z,ZL):
    y=Z*(ZL*f*np.cos(b*f)+i*Z*np.sin(b*f))/(Z*np.cos(b*f)+i*ZL*f*np.sin(b*f))
    return y.real

param, param_cov = curve_fit(loaded_re, f, z.real,bounds=((10,0,0),(np.inf,1000,1000)))
